"tin JIT vào tệp ``perf.data``.::"

#: ../../howto/perf_profiling.rst:239
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"$ perf record -F 9999 -g -k 1 --call-graph dwarf -o perf.data python -Xperf_jit my_script.py\n"
